{
  "texts": [
    "The dataset CKHK-22 comprises 24 class identifiers.",
    "These encompassed the following: barrettes, barrettesshort-segment, bbps-0-1, bbps-2-3, cecum, esophagitis-a, esophagitis-b-d, haemorrhoids, ileum, impacted stool, nonpolyps, polyps, pylorus, retroflex-rectum, retroflex-stomach, ulcerative colitis-grade 0-1, ulcerative colitis-grade 1, ulcerative colitis-grade 1-2, ulcerative colitis-grade 2, ulcerative colitis-grade 2-3, grade 3, and the z-line.",
    "We design the PolynetDWTCADx system to detect and segment colorectal cancer, while our more comprehensive set of labels covers a wider range of colorectal diseases and abnormalities.",
    "This provides a robust foundation for training and testing.",
    "Figure 2 illustrates sample images of the CKHK-22."
  ]
}